---
title: Campbell's Chicken Stuffing Bowls with Campbell's Concentrated Chicken Broth Sage Gravy
description: We all know everyone's favourite part of festive dinners is the stuffing, so why not have it for dinner? Our thyme chicken, apple and sweet potato stuffing bowl will have you longing to cozy up to a fireplace!
